								<span class="marathon-card__label">참가연령</span>
								<span class="marathon-card__value">유아, 아동, 청소년, 성인</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<UiButton
					variant="primary"
					text="참가신청"
					href="./마라톤모집-신청"
					size="large"
					className="marathon-card__button"
				/>
			</div>

			<!-- 마라톤 카드 4 -->
			<div class="marathon-card">
				<div class="marathon-card__header">
					<span class="marathon-card__index">4.</span>
					<div class="marathon-card__content">
						<h3 class="marathon-card__title">[2024년] 독서근력 키우기, 독서마라톤 코스 신청 2차</h3>
						<div class="marathon-card__info">
							<div class="marathon-card__info-row">
								<span class="marathon-card__label">신청기간</span>
								<span class="marathon-card__value">2025-01-01 ~ 2025-12-31</span>
